DRWP_no_w_comp.bin:
profiles 1,2,3,1771 from external large data file

DRWP_no_w_comp__prof_1771.csv:
A csv format of profile 1771 from DRWP_no_w_comp.bin

DRWP_w_comp.bin:
profiles 1,2,3,1771 from external large data file

DRWP_w_comp__prof_2.csv:
A csv format of profile 2 from DRWP_w_comp.bin

corrupt_binaries:
contains additional files used to test the binary reader fault detections.

ConvertBinToCsv.cpp:
Reads the binaries and writes a specific profile to a csv file.
